1025
00:33:35,922 --> 00:33:38,661
- All the prizes will disappear. - Yes.

1026
00:33:38,662 --> 00:33:40,791
The game gets difficult.

1027
00:33:40,792 --> 00:33:42,392
- Talk about it. - Think carefully.

1028
00:33:43,062 --> 00:33:45,102
- Can we get five seconds? - Of course.

1029
00:33:45,602 --> 00:33:47,132
- Five, - The two besties.

1030
00:33:47,232 --> 00:33:48,871
Four, three,

1031
00:33:48,872 --> 00:33:49,872
(What will the two decide?)

1032
00:33:49,873 --> 00:33:50,902
- two... - Okay.

1033
00:33:51,742 --> 00:33:53,611
Round 3. In 1, 2, 3.

1034
00:33:53,612 --> 00:33:54,642
- Go! - Go!

1035
00:33:55,242 --> 00:33:56,712
Why? Just why?

1036
00:33:56,912 --> 00:33:58,082
Aren't you being too greedy?

1037
00:33:58,342 --> 00:33:59,511
Hold on a second.

1038
00:33:59,512 --> 00:34:01,481
- Weren't we at a good spot to end? - It's...

1039
00:34:01,482 --> 00:34:03,852
We had just cheered and all that just now.

1040
00:34:04,282 --> 00:34:06,452
- Isn't it enough? - We have faith in ESom.

1041
00:34:07,052 --> 00:34:08,651
- Oh, no. - In Som and Kyung Nam?

1042
00:34:08,652 --> 00:34:10,391
- The two are improving... - This is bad.

1043
00:34:10,392 --> 00:34:11,422
If I'm being frank.

1044
00:34:12,022 --> 00:34:15,262
(What's Round 3's prize?)

1045
00:34:16,502 --> 00:34:17,531
- What is it? - What?

1046
00:34:17,532 --> 00:34:18,612
- What does it say? - What?

1047
00:34:19,102 --> 00:34:21,462
"Came to take photos and became friends before we knew it."

1048
00:34:21,732 --> 00:34:23,332
"It's become a haven for the customers."

1049
00:34:23,872 --> 00:34:25,842
"PlayStation Five Pro."

1050
00:34:26,512 --> 00:34:28,111
- A game console? - They're not allowed to go home.

1051
00:34:28,112 --> 00:34:29,812
It's already...

1052
00:34:29,942 --> 00:34:30,942
That console?

1053
00:34:30,943 --> 00:34:32,681
- The thing is... - Really?

1054
00:34:32,682 --> 00:34:34,251
(Cheering)

1055
00:34:34,252 --> 00:34:36,081
This is wrong.

1056
00:34:36,082 --> 00:34:37,221
- This is wrong. - With this,

1057
00:34:37,222 --> 00:34:38,482
you'll wreck a family.

1058
00:34:38,782 --> 00:34:40,421
Nobody will go home now.

1059
00:34:40,422 --> 00:34:41,422
This is wrong.

1060
00:34:42,222 --> 00:34:43,702
You're stopping them from going home.

1061
00:34:44,222 --> 00:34:45,892
This is really bad.

1062
00:34:47,092 --> 00:34:48,131
I'd love to win the prize for them.

1063
00:34:48,132 --> 00:34:49,401
What's Round Three?

1064
00:34:49,402 --> 00:34:50,801
(Round 3)

1065
00:34:50,802 --> 00:34:52,872
(An obstacle is placed in the middle.)

1066
00:34:54,372 --> 00:34:57,172
(Must aim while dodging the obstacle)

1067
00:34:57,272 --> 00:34:59,442
- I see. - We have to avoid the obstacle.

1068
00:34:59,872 --> 00:35:01,811
That means we can't aim from the center.

1069
00:35:01,812 --> 00:35:02,812
- Yes. - Correct.

1070
00:35:03,212 --> 00:35:04,612
From here or...

1071
00:35:05,682 --> 00:35:06,752
What?

1072
00:35:06,852 --> 00:35:08,611
- What? - He's got it.

1073
00:35:08,612 --> 00:35:09,681
- I knew it. - I'll finish us off.

1074
00:35:09,682 --> 00:35:12,121
- He needs a hurdle to overcome. - We've got it.

1075
00:35:12,122 --> 00:35:13,321
- Right there. - Yes, right here.

1076
00:35:13,322 --> 00:35:14,522
- Right there. - Right here.

1077
00:35:14,952 --> 00:35:17,161
- Mark it with a pen. - It's right here, Suk Ho.

1078
00:35:17,162 --> 00:35:18,692
- Exactly. - All right.

1079
00:35:19,162 --> 00:35:21,192
- Let's imagine that doesn't exist. - Yes.

1080
00:35:21,892 --> 00:35:22,902
- We've got it. - Nice.

1081
00:35:23,732 --> 00:35:24,862
See that? I've got it.

1082
00:35:25,202 --> 00:35:27,672
- Right there. - There's a reason you're Jae Suk.

1083
00:35:28,302 --> 00:35:29,841
- You're good at it. - I knew it.

1084
00:35:29,842 --> 00:35:31,471
- Let's cheer. - I think we'll succeed.

1085
00:35:31,472 --> 00:35:32,472
(Let's try Round 3!)

1086
00:35:32,473 --> 00:35:33,571
In 1, 2, 3.

1087
00:35:33,572 --> 00:35:34,612
- Let's go! - Let's go!

1088
00:35:34,812 --> 00:35:36,442
- Okay. - Good luck.

1089
00:35:37,012 --> 00:35:38,541
- All right. - The eighth try.

1090
00:35:38,542 --> 00:35:39,681
- Here I go. - Okay.

1091
00:35:39,682 --> 00:35:41,151
- Ready. - He'll get one.

1092
00:35:41,152 --> 00:35:42,152
Set.

1093
00:35:42,822 --> 00:35:44,081
(8th try)

1094
00:35:44,082 --> 00:35:45,162
- My gosh! - What happened?

1095
00:35:46,992 --> 00:35:48,392
(Shot another 2 birds with 1 stone)

1096
00:35:49,022 --> 00:35:50,091
- What? - What?

1097
00:35:50,092 --> 00:35:51,892
(2 were shot, but 1 still has to fall down.)

1098
00:35:51,992 --> 00:35:53,131
- What? - What?

1099
00:35:53,132 --> 00:35:54,231
(Please fall down!)

1100
00:35:54,232 --> 00:35:55,462
What?

1101
00:35:56,362 --> 00:35:57,802
If only that falls down!

1102
00:35:59,572 --> 00:36:01,232
- Come on! - It's gone!

1103
00:36:01,432 --> 00:36:02,971
- Okay! - You did it!

1104
00:36:02,972 --> 00:36:04,472
- Hurry! - Goodness!

1105
00:36:04,842 --> 00:36:07,442
- What just happened? Seriously. - You did it!

1106
00:36:07,642 --> 00:36:09,341
- What was that? - Calm down.

1107
00:36:09,342 --> 00:36:11,711
Jae Suk, it's your track.

1108
00:36:11,712 --> 00:36:12,811
Stay calm.

1109
00:36:12,812 --> 00:36:13,912
It's the track you used.

1110
00:36:14,482 --> 00:36:16,451
- Come. - We've got plenty of time.

1111
00:36:16,452 --> 00:36:18,451
- Who's next? Me? It's me. - It's okay.

1112
00:36:18,452 --> 00:36:20,351
I'm going to finish us off.

1113
00:36:20,352 --> 00:36:22,491
No rush. Take your time.

1114
00:36:22,492 --> 00:36:23,521
- I will finish us off! - Som.

1115
00:36:23,522 --> 00:36:25,661
- Som. - Ten seconds left.

1116
00:36:25,662 --> 00:36:27,261
- Ten seconds. - Oh, dear.

1117
00:36:27,262 --> 00:36:28,962
- Okay. - Stand by.

1118
00:36:29,462 --> 00:36:30,732
- Go from there. - Five,

1119
00:36:32,632 --> 00:36:34,202
- four, three... - Hit it.

1120
00:36:38,642 --> 00:36:39,642
Five...

1121
00:36:40,512 --> 00:36:43,582
(Possessed by the deity of games)

1122
00:36:44,582 --> 00:36:47,551
Unbelievable! She's unbelievable!

1123
00:36:47,552 --> 00:36:48,852
- Som! - For real.

1124
00:36:49,012 --> 00:36:50,221
Seriously.

1125
00:36:50,222 --> 00:36:52,321
- Som. - Suk Ho didn't even play.

1126
00:36:52,322 --> 00:36:53,322
I didn't.

1127
00:36:53,452 --> 00:36:55,192
- Thank you. - I didn't.

1128
00:36:56,692 --> 00:36:58,791
(Kyung Nam's perfect 2 birds with 1 stone...)

1129
00:36:58,792 --> 00:37:00,691
(and Ace Som finishing it off)

1130
00:37:00,692 --> 00:37:02,261
Som is on a roll.

1131
00:37:02,262 --> 00:37:04,131
- Good job. - Round Three,

1132
00:37:04,132 --> 00:37:05,201
- success! - Success!

1133
00:37:05,202 --> 00:37:06,202
(Round 3, success)

1134
00:37:06,203 --> 00:37:07,332
Success!

1135
00:37:07,732 --> 00:37:09,701
Take it. We had one coin left.

1136
00:37:09,702 --> 00:37:10,971
Really.

1137
00:37:10,972 --> 00:37:12,041
- That was a real drama. - You see...

1138
00:37:12,042 --> 00:37:13,111
- Som. - This is so exciting.

1139
00:37:13,112 --> 00:37:14,341
She aims for the buzzer-beater.

1140
00:37:14,342 --> 00:37:16,182
- Five, four, three, two, one. - Actually,

1141
00:37:16,342 --> 00:37:18,541
Suk Ho was left,

1142
00:37:18,542 --> 00:37:20,211
- but she used up all the time. - Nice.

1143
00:37:20,212 --> 00:37:21,851
She's a real clutch performer.

1144
00:37:21,852 --> 00:37:23,681
(Clutch performer Som's determination)

1145
00:37:23,682 --> 00:37:26,792
- Hiking up Yeonjuam was worth it. - The energy was from Yeonjuam.

1146
00:37:27,522 --> 00:37:29,122
Let's get moving while she still has it.

1147
00:37:31,022 --> 00:37:32,261
- Chung Rok. - Yes?

1148
00:37:32,262 --> 00:37:33,561
- You must go home. - Of course.

1149
00:37:33,562 --> 00:37:34,632
I'll go home.

1150
00:37:34,962 --> 00:37:36,201
I'll install it at my house.

1151
00:37:36,202 --> 00:37:37,961
Once again, congratulations.

1152
00:37:37,962 --> 00:37:39,672
- Well done. - Thank you.

1153
00:37:40,172 --> 00:37:41,201
To think we'd leave on a good note.

1154
00:37:41,202 --> 00:37:42,432
How nice.

1155
00:37:47,812 --> 00:37:49,341
Amazing.

1156
00:37:49,342 --> 00:37:51,381
- That was incredible. - Let's leave after checking...

1157
00:37:51,382 --> 00:37:52,582
- the next place. - Okay.

1158
00:37:53,112 --> 00:37:54,481
I'm sorry you had no turn.

1159
00:37:54,482 --> 00:37:55,512
Don't worry about it.

1160
00:37:56,052 --> 00:37:58,251
- No, it's okay. - Really.

1161
00:37:58,252 --> 00:37:59,421
I don't even need to play.

1162
00:37:59,422 --> 00:38:00,821
(Laughing)

1163
00:38:00,822 --> 00:38:02,382
I'd love to give my turn to the others.

1164
00:38:02,422 --> 00:38:03,422
Nice.

1165
00:38:03,423 --> 00:38:05,361
All right, let's check out our second Whenever Guest.

1166
00:38:05,362 --> 00:38:06,762
- "Lee Ok Soon." - Sorry?

1167
00:38:07,562 --> 00:38:10,531
"Opened in the same year as Children's Grand Park,"

1168
00:38:10,532 --> 00:38:13,331
"I've watched children go on dates..."

1169
00:38:13,332 --> 00:38:14,702
"and get married for 54 years."

1170
00:38:15,102 --> 00:38:18,501
"I'm very grateful they visit even after graduating."

1171
00:38:18,502 --> 00:38:22,541
"At tables filled with feasts of memories all the time,"

1172
00:38:22,542 --> 00:38:25,141
"come have some snacks Whenever Possible."

1173
00:38:25,142 --> 00:38:26,781
It must be... You know.

1174
00:38:26,782 --> 00:38:30,482
- She must sell snacks for drinks. - Right?

1175
00:38:30,722 --> 00:38:33,002
- It must be a restaurant. - What time must we get there?

1176
00:38:33,052 --> 00:38:34,191
By 2pm.

1177
00:38:34,192 --> 00:38:36,121
- We've got time. - We have some time to kill.

1178
00:38:36,122 --> 00:38:38,491
- Let's go eat. - Yes, we should get lunch.

1179
00:38:38,492 --> 00:38:40,731
- I'm excited about today. - If it's Neung-dong,

1180
00:38:40,732 --> 00:38:42,331
- isn't it near Gunja? - Sejong University...

1181
00:38:42,332 --> 00:38:43,532
is in Neung-dong.

1182
00:38:44,232 --> 00:38:45,502
The scheme is...

1183
00:38:46,932 --> 00:38:48,071
Yeon Seok is...

1184
00:38:48,072 --> 00:38:49,131
Isn't it the school cafeteria?

1185
00:38:49,132 --> 00:38:51,132
(The second spare time is near Sejong University.)

1186
00:38:51,172 --> 00:38:52,941
- Okay. - It's gotten warmer than earlier.

1187
00:38:52,942 --> 00:38:54,172
- Right? A lot warmer. - Yes.

1188
00:38:54,342 --> 00:38:55,871
Maybe we're all warmed up.

1189
00:38:55,872 --> 00:38:57,241
That might be true.

1190
00:38:57,242 --> 00:38:59,712
- Som, you were amazing. - Thank you.

1191
00:38:59,852 --> 00:39:01,492
- You too, Kyung Nam. - You surprised us.

1192
00:39:01,882 --> 00:39:02,921
I guess our drama...

1193
00:39:02,922 --> 00:39:04,202
- will be a big hit. - For real.

1194
00:39:06,322 --> 00:39:08,642
You knocked all of them down as if possessed by something.

1195
00:39:09,722 --> 00:39:11,491
- I was possessed. - I had to be possessed...

1196
00:39:11,492 --> 00:39:13,262
in the drama,

1197
00:39:13,592 --> 00:39:15,491
- I was possessed. - but today,

1198
00:39:15,492 --> 00:39:18,101
you were possessed by a sniper or something.

1199
00:39:18,102 --> 00:39:19,931
- That was amazing concentration. - "I'll wrap it up."

1200
00:39:19,932 --> 00:39:21,272
- Exactly. - Right?

1201
00:39:22,272 --> 00:39:23,741
We have to ride Bus 422.

1202
00:39:23,742 --> 00:39:25,262
- Bus 422. - It's coming in 2 minutes.

1203
00:39:25,302 --> 00:39:26,512
- Bus 422? - Yes.

1204
00:39:27,742 --> 00:39:29,311
- It's... - For lunch,

1205
00:39:29,312 --> 00:39:30,811
- let's have whatever our ace wants. - Okay.

1206
00:39:30,812 --> 00:39:31,912
- Yes. - I'm in.

1207
00:39:32,342 --> 00:39:35,082
Is there a list of must-eat places?

1208
00:39:35,312 --> 00:39:36,822
I'll look one up.

1209
00:39:37,752 --> 00:39:39,021
- There are plenty. - We'll eat...

1210
00:39:39,022 --> 00:39:40,422
whatever you want.

1211
00:39:41,322 --> 00:39:43,761
- We're not the type to queue up. - The two of us did nothing.

1212
00:39:43,762 --> 00:39:46,021
- You have to queue up. - A short while is fine.

1213
00:39:46,022 --> 00:39:47,731
If the winner wants to queue up,

1214
00:39:47,732 --> 00:39:48,791
- we must. - True.

1215
00:39:48,792 --> 00:39:51,432
- We must. - Even so, we'll queue up if needed.

1216
00:39:52,102 --> 00:39:54,102
Kyung Nam shooting 2 birds with 1 stone was...

1217
00:39:54,202 --> 00:39:55,472
- Right. - For real.

1218
00:39:55,672 --> 00:39:57,841
- Wasn't it twice? - It's being forgotten.

1219
00:39:57,842 --> 00:39:59,972
The three of you did great.

1220
00:40:00,442 --> 00:40:01,911
- Me too? - Yes.

1221
00:40:01,912 --> 00:40:04,072
- We passed Round 1 because of you. - You did Round 1.

1222
00:40:04,142 --> 00:40:05,212
When?

1223
00:40:06,042 --> 00:40:08,451
Jae Suk, why won't you remember it?

1224
00:40:08,452 --> 00:40:10,381
- Suk Ho finished off Round One. - He did.

1225
00:40:10,382 --> 00:40:11,421
Suk Ho did.

1226
00:40:11,422 --> 00:40:13,092
- It was amazing. - Yes.

1227
00:40:13,252 --> 00:40:14,522
I'm serious.

1228
00:40:14,752 --> 00:40:16,462
Really. It's here.

1229
00:40:16,922 --> 00:40:17,961
Hi.

1230
00:40:17,962 --> 00:40:19,292
- Hi. - Hi.

1231
00:40:19,792 --> 00:40:21,092
- Hi. - Hi.

1232
00:40:22,232 --> 00:40:24,761
- I'm beat after one game. - Right?

1233
00:40:24,762 --> 00:40:26,031
You use up a lot of energy.

1234
00:40:26,032 --> 00:40:28,402
You don't get excited that much on a regular day.

1235
00:40:28,602 --> 00:40:30,172
I doubt I'll get any sleep.

1236
00:40:31,542 --> 00:40:33,141
No wonder Yeon Seok takes time off for this show...

1237
00:40:33,142 --> 00:40:34,172
during our drama shoot.

1238
00:40:34,412 --> 00:40:36,241
- He's addicted. - Yes, it's the thrill.

1239
00:40:36,242 --> 00:40:37,381
A game addict.

1240
00:40:37,382 --> 00:40:38,888
(Yeon Seok has recharged in his spare time.)

1241
00:40:38,912 --> 00:40:41,481
There was a time I came for this show...

1242
00:40:41,482 --> 00:40:43,552
after an all-nighter drama shoot.

1243
00:40:43,682 --> 00:40:45,582
- Once I get here, - I remember.

1244
00:40:45,922 --> 00:40:47,822
Despite only getting 1 to 2 hours of sleep...

1245
00:40:48,022 --> 00:40:49,761
- Wasn't it enough? - Yes, the dopamine rush was...

1246
00:40:49,762 --> 00:40:52,091
You even played games at our drama set.

1247
00:40:52,092 --> 00:40:53,191
- He brought a ping-pong ball. - We had a bet...

1248
00:40:53,192 --> 00:40:55,261
- Yes. - with ice creams in between.

1249
00:40:55,262 --> 00:40:57,622
- With the production team. - Yes, playing ping-pong balls.

1250
00:40:57,732 --> 00:40:59,532
You need to get rehab.

1251
00:40:59,902 --> 00:41:01,102
What rehab?

1252
00:41:01,332 --> 00:41:03,372
- Because I'm addicted to dopamine? - Yes.

1253
00:41:04,102 --> 00:41:05,241
- Last time... - All right, Som.

1254
00:41:05,242 --> 00:41:06,972
Choose today's lunch menu.

1255
00:41:07,672 --> 00:41:09,342
There seem to be many gukbap places.

1256
00:41:09,572 --> 00:41:11,912
Since Som is feeling gukbap today,

1257
00:41:12,282 --> 00:41:13,851
- We should get gukbap. - let's get gukbap.

1258
00:41:13,852 --> 00:41:14,882
Or udon?

1259
00:41:15,212 --> 00:41:16,381
- Udon. - Udon sounds good.

1260
00:41:16,382 --> 00:41:17,921
- I like udon. - There's an udon place.

1261
00:41:17,922 --> 00:41:19,052
- Right? - Yes.

1262
00:41:19,252 --> 00:41:21,792
The rest should stay quiet and not voice their opinions.

1263
00:41:23,822 --> 00:41:24,922
- Even if... - Got it?

1264
00:41:25,422 --> 00:41:26,861
She wants cold red bean bingsu,

1265
00:41:26,862 --> 00:41:27,938
- we have to eat it. - Exactly.

1266
00:41:27,962 --> 00:41:30,302
We must eat ice cream if that's what she wants for lunch.

1267
00:41:31,102 --> 00:41:33,232
In Hwayang-dong,

1268
00:41:33,572 --> 00:41:36,331
there's a really famous ramen place...

1269
00:41:36,332 --> 00:41:37,802
near the front of Konkuk University.

1270
00:41:38,072 --> 00:41:39,141
- Hey. - Don't talk.

1271
00:41:39,142 --> 00:41:41,172
- Don't talk. - I'm just giving her an idea.

1272
00:41:41,972 --> 00:41:43,641
- Jong. - Jong.

1273
00:41:43,642 --> 00:41:45,412
- What's "Jong" from? - Jong. Sejong.

1274
00:41:45,582 --> 00:41:46,611
Jong? Got it.

1275
00:41:46,612 --> 00:41:48,211
- Is your name "Jong" in the drama? - No.

1276
00:41:48,212 --> 00:41:49,852
- Sejong University. - Sejong University.

1277
00:41:50,382 --> 00:41:52,082
Jong.

1278
00:41:52,652 --> 00:41:54,551
