It's okay. I'm honored.

2565
01:24:58,812 --> 01:25:00,751
- We're sorry. - Gosh, it's okay.

2566
01:25:00,752 --> 01:25:02,792
I got to meet all the celebrities I wanted to meet.

2567
01:25:02,822 --> 01:25:03,952
Now,

2568
01:25:04,352 --> 01:25:06,651
- we need to promote the drama. - Okay.

2569
01:25:06,652 --> 01:25:08,452
That came out of nowhere!

2570
01:25:09,462 --> 01:25:10,991
(The mindset of a professional emcee)

2571
01:25:10,992 --> 01:25:13,431
You can't do that in this atmosphere.

2572
01:25:13,432 --> 01:25:15,732
(How will you promote our drama in this atmosphere?)

2573
01:25:15,862 --> 01:25:17,432
I don't know.

2574
01:25:17,502 --> 01:25:19,331
I need to go home and lie down.

2575
01:25:19,332 --> 01:25:20,831
- I feel so dizzy. - I'll watch the drama diligently.

2576
01:25:20,832 --> 01:25:22,571
Okay. The drama will begin airing soon.

2577
01:25:22,572 --> 01:25:24,541
- It's Professor Ahn's drama. - Exactly.

2578
01:25:24,542 --> 01:25:25,811
- I'll watch the drama diligently. - Okay.

2579
01:25:25,812 --> 01:25:26,972
I'm satisfied.

2580
01:25:27,342 --> 01:25:29,081
- While it's unfortunate... - We did our best.

2581
01:25:29,082 --> 01:25:31,242
We did our best. Let's give a round of applause...

2582
01:25:31,342 --> 01:25:33,851
to the three actors and the owner who joined us. Thank you.

2583
01:25:33,852 --> 01:25:34,852
(Please watch "Phantom Lawyer" at 9:50pm on Fridays and Saturdays.)

2584
01:25:34,853 --> 01:25:36,822
Thank you. It's so unfortunate.

2585
01:25:37,022 --> 01:25:39,022
- It's so unfortunate. - I'll visit for sure.

2586
01:25:39,192 --> 01:25:41,191
(A chilly vibe hits "Whenever Possible.")

2587
01:25:41,192 --> 01:25:44,022
(Park Sung Woong)

2588
01:25:44,092 --> 01:25:45,761
(Lee Sang Yun)

2589
01:25:45,762 --> 01:25:47,291
(Why did you change your tactic after hitting it like this?)

2590
01:25:47,292 --> 01:25:48,692
(I need to practice.)

2591
01:25:48,892 --> 01:25:50,361
(Playing a game as if he's studying)

2592
01:25:50,362 --> 01:25:51,962
(I haven't gotten the deposit yet.)

2593
01:25:52,232 --> 01:25:53,401
(What deposit?)

2594
01:25:53,402 --> 01:25:56,202
(Shooting a variety show like film noir)

2595
01:25:56,402 --> 01:25:57,801
(I see that there's an assassination attempt today.)

2596
01:25:57,802 --> 01:26:00,872
(Charismatic Whenever Friends are here.)

2597
01:26:03,412 --> 01:26:06,652
(They become timid before the game.)

2598
01:26:06,852 --> 01:26:08,952
(What are you guys doing?)

2599
01:26:09,182 --> 01:26:10,352
(I'm... I'm sorry.)

2600
01:26:10,522 --> 01:26:12,491
(The Whenever Friends are pitiful despite their charismatic looks.)

2601
01:26:12,492 --> 01:26:14,152
The two of them are the worst.

2602
01:26:14,222 --> 01:26:15,761
(The film noir vibe is nowhere to be found.)

2603
01:26:15,762 --> 01:26:16,792
(Sighing)

2604
01:26:17,222 --> 01:26:18,791
(Jae Suk, just finish it!)

2605
01:26:18,792 --> 01:26:20,592
(Is Jae Suk the only one they can depend on?)

2606
01:26:21,092 --> 01:26:22,231
Today is your day!

2607
01:26:22,232 --> 01:26:24,002
(Today is Jae Suk's day.)

2608
01:26:24,562 --> 01:26:25,902
(Thank you.)

2609
01:26:26,032 --> 01:26:27,902
(The weather is perfect for giving out gifts.)

2610
01:26:28,132 --> 01:26:29,902
(Whenever Possible)
